{"data": [{"id": "4743702", "title": "How Investors Should Assess The Potential Walgreens Buyout", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Walgreens\" data-id=\"458977889\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">RiverNorthPhotography</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>With around two weeks left until the tax-loss selling opportunity ends, Walgreens Boots Alliance (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WBA\" title=\"Walgreens Boots Alliance, Inc.\">WBA</a></span>) unexpectedly soared by 18% to nearly $11.00 on December 10, 2024. The WSJ reported that Walgreens and Sycamore Partners <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4383274-walgreens-jumps-on-report-of-talks-to-sell-itself-to-sycamore-partners\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4383274-walgreens-jumps-on-report-of-talks-to-sell-itself-to-sycamore-partners\" target=\"_blank\">held discussions about a</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458977889/image_458977889.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743702-how-investors-should-assess-the-potential-walgreens-buyout", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 01:19:35"}, {"id": "4743700", "title": "ImmunityBio's Cash Burn And Dilution Dampen Anktiva's Potential", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Red liquid in drinking glass\" data-id=\"1272819028\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5765px\" height=\"5295px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jonathan Knowles</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>My last update on <b>ImmunityBio, Inc. </b>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IBRX\" title=\"ImmunityBio, Inc.\">IBRX</a></span>) followed the FDA-approval of Anktiva (nogapendekin alfa inbakicept) for the treatment of BCG-unresponsive non-muscle invasive bladder cancer (NMIBC). I conducted a discounted cash flow analysis that valued Anktiva at $2.3 billion (net present value) based on a 50% market share</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272819028/image_1272819028.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743700-immunitybios-cash-burn-and-dilution-dampen-anktivas-potential", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 01:11:11"}, {"id": "4743699", "title": "Nvidia: Earnings Fail To Impress Again", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nvidia headquarters in Santa Clara, California, USA\" data-id=\"1547214730\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Nvidia Corporation</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a></span>) easily beat the estimates in the recent <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4313935-nvidia-non-gaap-eps-of-0_81-beats-0_06-revenue-of-35_08b-beats-1_95b\">quarterly earnings report</a>. The company reported EPS of $0.81 which beat estimates by a whopping 8.5%. However, we did not see any positive momentum in the stock. A similar</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743699-nvidia-earnings-fail-to-impress-again", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 01:03:58"}, {"id": "4743697", "title": "Topicus: The Latest Price Dip Presents A Buying Opportunity", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1497787694/image_1497787694.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Perfect connection on business meeting!\" data-id=\"1497787694\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1497787694/image_1497787694.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1497787694/image_1497787694.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1497787694/image_1497787694.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1497787694/image_1497787694.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1497787694/image_1497787694.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1497787694/image_1497787694.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1497787694/image_1497787694.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1497787694/image_1497787694.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">skynesher</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This is a follow-up article to an earlier coverage of Topicus (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">TSXV:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TOI:CA\" title=\"Topicus.com Inc.\">TOI:CA</a></span>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TOITF\" title=\"Topicus.com Inc.\">OTCPK:TOITF</a>) with a recommended \"buy\" rating. The stock has been relatively stable since that publication (in May) and currently trades around the price at publication of that article, after experiencing</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1497787694/image_1497787694.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743697-topicus-latest-price-dip-presents-buying-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 00:58:15"}, {"id": "4743696", "title": "Pfizer: Peer-Leading Dividend And Potential Substantial Shareholder Returns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s