4031.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743696-pfizer-stock-peer-leading-dividend-potential-substantial-shareholder-returns", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 00:50:22"}, {"id": "4743691", "title": "CVS: Why I'm Selling My Worst Holding Of 2024", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170617525/image_170617525.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Patient after carpal tunnel syndrome operation at plastic surgery\" data-id=\"170617525\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170617525/image_170617525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170617525/image_170617525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170617525/image_170617525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170617525/image_170617525.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170617525/image_170617525.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170617525/image_170617525.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170617525/image_170617525.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170617525/image_170617525.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">choja</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I sold my modest-sized (2% of portfolio) position in CVS (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CVS\" title=\"CVS Health Corporation\">CVS</a></span>) today. I've held it in varying sizes for much of this year. Ultimately, I closed it to clinch my very worst position experience of 2024. And as is my nature, I'm happy to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/170617525/image_170617525.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743691-cvs-why-im-selling-my-worst-holding-of-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 00:14:36"}, {"id": "4743689", "title": "Coherent: Boosted By A Reliable Leadership Team And An Exciting Future", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163653396/image_2163653396.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"AI chat icons\" data-id=\"2163653396\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163653396/image_2163653396.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163653396/image_2163653396.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163653396/image_2163653396.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163653396/image_2163653396.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163653396/image_2163653396.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163653396/image_2163653396.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163653396/image_2163653396.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163653396/image_2163653396.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>Coherent Corp. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COHR\" title=\"Coherent Corp.\">COHR</a></span>), a vertically integrated electronic component manufacturer, whose products are primarily used in the communications and industrial markets, has been in tremendous form through 2024. On a YTD basis, we\u2019ve seen the stock more than double, and generate total returns that</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163653396/image_2163653396.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743689-coherent-boosted-by-a-reliable-leadership-team-and-an-exciting-future", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 00:04:57"}, {"id": "4743687", "title": "BlackRock: Moving Aggressively Into New Segments", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492670838/image_1492670838.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"BlackRock HQ in New York City\" data-id=\"1492670838\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492670838/image_1492670838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492670838/image_1492670838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492670838/image_1492670838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492670838/image_1492670838.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492670838/image_1492670838.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492670838/image_1492670838.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty